Hello id like to apply for the add ad credits feature

Hi Ameriyae, you can add ad credits by following these steps:
1. Access the Billing Section.
2. Under Ad Credits, click on ‘Add ad credits.'
3. Choose ‘Customize’ and enter the total value of your gifted ad credit, plus at least $1.
4. Enter the promotional code.
5. Provide credit card information and check out.
For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17391456255629-How-to-redeem-a-NewsBreak-ad-credit). Let me know if you need any further assistance!
